item.dc:creator: @davidi2 Davidi2
item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

[quote=“SenQi, post:2, topic:338191”]public static RSString aRSString_959 = Class112.stringToRSString(43, “RuneScape is loading )2 please wait)3)3)3”);
in Class48 on my version of the client, just search your java files for the text=s[/quote]Correct.

I would just like to point out that the )# parts are the special characters.

)2 = -
)3 = .
